data.description: This beautiful 3 bedrooms / 2 bathrooms in a quiet gated community has all the upgrades you are looking for!! The open floor plan leads you into a completely upgraded kitchen that features a center island for extra counter space, granite countertops and 42" cabinets, and plenty of storage. Also, includes gas stove, stainless steel appliances, upgraded faucets.  You will fall in love with this kitchen. Unwind in your private oasis, the master suite, with generous space, a walk-in closet, and an in-suite bathroom.  You will also see the custom-made window blinds throughout. Other upgrades include granite countertops in both bathrooms, an alarm system, irrigation system, water heater, a garage opener with two remote controls.  When not enjoying the community club house and pool, you can enjoy entertaining in the lovely backyard complete with vinyl privacy fencing and a covered sitting area. Come see this charming Florida Home where sunshine living awaits! Discover the allure of Florida living with this delightful home in the heart of Winter Haven. Positioned between Tampa and Orlando, you're within reach of world-famous theme parks, cultural attractions, and a variety of entertainment options. Winter Haven lives up to its name with numerous lakes for boating, fishing, and water sports. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to make this wonderful property your home.
